Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: New York immigrants
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wwvq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 3 Oct 1982
Massive increase of immgrants arriving into New York widens the ethnic mix of the city. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less